title: Chuchik Toys Magnapad Magnetic Drawing Board – Interactive Alphabet Letter Tracing Board Game for Ages 3-5 – Portable Kids Writing Board and 2 Pen Magnets for Educational Play and Alphabet Games
feature_bullets: [" AMAZING FROM A TO Z – Immerse your child in educational play with this magnetic drawing board! With easy-to-follow arrows, numbered steps, and color-coded letters, your toddler drawing board makes it easy to practice writing and build fundamental skills!"," ENTRANCING EDUCATION – Make learning to write a blast with some magnetic magic! Watch your child’s delight as beads appear on the surface of each letter with the touch of a red or blue magnet pen. A swipe of a hand makes the beads disappear, just like that!"," PORTABLE PLAY – Never stop learning with Chuchik Toys’ portable abc games! At just 12.4 x 10 x 0.43 in., your magnetic drawing board is a convenient size for slipping in a backpack and taking on long car rides, to restaurants, or to a friend’s house!"," BOUNTIFUL BENEFITS – Writing skills aren’t all your child will develop with our alphabet learning toys! Following the numbered arrows helps your child learn to follow directions. Grasping the pen to write, tracing with their fingers, and swiping with their hand to erase, hones valuable fine motor skills!"," TRACE OUR PROMISE – Delight in learning letters with a colorful, interactive board that’s built to last for years of fun!
